05:46.024 --> 05:48.446
- Are you all right, Father?
- It's a little out of tune.

05:52.759 --> 05:54.252
Father?

05:54.319 --> 05:56.251
You know I've always been devout.

05:56.358 --> 05:58.226
I've...

05:59.329 --> 06:03.693
I believe in the Bible.
I live life by His word...

06:05.096 --> 06:06.980
