06:07.714 --> 06:09.634
Do you think
you lost your faith, Father?

06:09.701 --> 06:11.135
Lose my faith? How could I?

06:11.202 --> 06:12.527
I've just seen a demon appear

06:12.558 --> 06:14.191
and the smoke rising from the pit

06:14.253 --> 06:16.774
to torment mankind
just as it's written in Gospel.

06:17.317 --> 06:19.801
I'm not scared
because I'm losing my faith.

06:20.039 --> 06:23.137
I'm scared because
it's stronger than ever.

06:31.956 --> 06:33.858
If we were judged right now,

06:33.925 --> 06:35.693
how many under our roof would burn?

06:36.801 --> 06:38.136
Would Mrs. Raven?

06:38.429 --> 06:41.293
Or will God forgive her
because she's gone crazy?

06:41.466 --> 06:42.734
Would the Chief?

06:42.800 --> 06:44.335
We've all seen his pride.

06:46.971 --> 06:48.473
Would you?

06:53.589 --> 06:54.712
Would you?

06:56.648 --> 06:58.040
The more I believe,

06:58.117 --> 07:02.087
the more I know it's my
responsibility to save them...

07:04.455 --> 07:07.058
and I've never been more afraid.

07:09.060 --> 07:10.662
Are you there?

07:13.064 --> 07:14.933
Are you there?

07:15.066 --> 07:16.267
Are you there?

07:16.334 --> 07:17.735
Who are you looking for, Natalie?

07:17.802 --> 07:19.170
I don't know yet.

07:22.840 --> 07:25.076
Friends, would you gather, please?

07:31.578 --> 07:33.852
- Mrs. Raven?
- Mm, not right now.

07:38.289 --> 07:41.593
Most of you have been
coming here for years.

07:42.074 --> 07:46.097
Most of you know me, just as
I know you and your families.

07:47.131 --> 07:50.563
