07:52.133 --> 07:53.914
- preach.
- Mm-hm.

07:55.940 --> 07:58.209
Instead, I will talk to you here.

08:02.046 --> 08:04.277
I believe Judgment Day has come.

08:05.675 --> 08:07.626
And I'm... I'm laughing,

08:07.681 --> 08:10.095
because I... I watch TV.

08:10.149 --> 08:13.424
I... I like baseball.

08:13.491 --> 08:14.759
I...

08:16.127 --> 08:17.629
I listen to music.

08:17.695 --> 08:19.797
I have a beer every now and then.

08:19.864 --> 08:21.656
I'm not the Judgment Day kind of guy.

08:21.701 --> 08:23.136
You know that.

08:25.703 --> 08:29.274
And yet, here we are.

08:31.075 --> 08:32.150
I hope I'm wrong.

08:32.197 --> 08:34.563
I hope the police get here to save us.

08:34.691 --> 08:36.549
But until then,

08:36.988 --> 08:41.458
I will do whatever I can
to help save your souls...

08:42.520 --> 08:43.922
pray with you.

08:48.488 --> 08:49.956
Mrs. Raven, please.

08:50.815 --> 08:53.471
That's very sweet, Father,
but there's really no need.

08:54.073 --> 08:56.334
The moth is a good friend of mine.

08:59.771 --> 09:03.140
And how is that possible?

09:03.679 --> 09:05.914
We met in my garden the other day.

09:06.328 --> 09:08.414
She landed on my hand.

09:08.666 --> 09:11.297
Will you care to explain to us

09:11.806 --> 09:13.508
what it was doing here, then?

09:14.332 --> 09:16.066
I don't know,

09:16.401 --> 09:17.965
but I'll find out.

09:23.023 --> 09:24.158
Are you there?

09:37.107 --> 09:38.942
I didn't see any cars out there.

09:50.889 --> 09:52.323
There's nothing in here, either.

09:58.630 --> 10:00.532
Maybe this guy will give us a ride.

10:36.271 --> 10:38.451
Any way to get any gas out of those?

10:38.596 --> 10:40.443
I wouldn't want to be out there
long enough to find out.

10:42.508 --> 10:44.177
You're Eve's husband, right?

10:48.280 --> 10:49.281
Yeah.

10:49.347 --> 10:50.782
You know where she is?

10:52.617 --> 10:54.052
I'm sorry.

10:56.688 --> 10:57.656
I'm Clay.

10:57.722 --> 10:59.191
Kevin.

10:59.257 --> 11:02.661
I had a kid in her class. I have a...

11:04.029 --> 11:06.232
He was outside when all this happened.

11:06.464 --> 11:08.967
He's safe somewhere. I know it.
I just gotta find him.

11:09.949 --> 11:11.317
I'm sure he is.

11:13.948 --> 11:15.073
Have you seen him?

11:26.952 --> 11:28.382
No.

11:28.812 --> 11:30.155
Sorry.

11:55.858 --> 11:57.293
You should, uh...

11:57.516 --> 12:00.428
You should stay here, get some rest.

12:01.753 --> 12:03.955
I haven't slept in two days.

12:05.824 --> 12:08.527
You can, uh, put it in the garage.

12:28.480 --> 12:31.447
Please tell me why we're lying
to this poor bastard.

12:31.947 --> 12:33.718
We should tell him.

12:35.020 --> 12:36.510
He has a working car,

12:36.564 --> 12:39.776
and in case you haven't noticed,
we're kinda stuck here.

12:40.643 --> 12:42.042
It's your wife and kid.

12:42.651 --> 12:44.604
Like you care about them.

12:48.567 --> 12:50.435
I'll talk to him.
I'll get him to take us.

12:50.502 --> 12:51.736
Good.

12:51.803 --> 12:53.238
You gonna keep your mouth shut?

12:53.305 --> 12:54.987
I don't know.
Are you gonna convince him?

13:09.647 --> 13:11.923
Oh. I'm sorry.
I didn't know you were here.

13:11.990 --> 13:13.787
Uh...

13:14.534 --> 13:16.013
it's okay.

13:17.195 --> 13:19.364
I guess you think I'm crazy as well.

13:20.765 --> 13:22.834
- Kind of.
- Mm, I may be,

13:22.901 --> 13:26.104
but I can see you're not yourself.

13:26.171 --> 13:27.172
Can I do anything?

13:28.273 --> 13:29.474
They took my gun.

13:32.377 --> 13:33.945
I don't think they'll rob a bank.

13:35.514 --> 13:37.314
I just let three prisoners escape

13:37.378 --> 13:39.246
in front of the whole church.

13:39.384 --> 13:41.080
So what?

13:41.386 --> 13:43.288
It's my job to enforce the law.

13:43.355 --> 13:47.682
Oh, the law is just people
trying to control human nature,

13:47.959 --> 13:49.604
as if that were possible.

13:49.704 --> 13:53.074
No one can do that, not even you.

13:55.901 --> 13:57.569
Thanks, Natalie.

14:00.238 --> 14:03.417
There will be food soon, if you want.

14:09.648 --> 14:10.749
Natalie?

14:10.930 --> 14:14.250
Uh, I think my presence
makes Father Romanov uncomfortable.

14:16.454 --> 14:17.856
I insist.

14:27.410 --> 14:29.111
You need to eat, honey.

14:29.256 --> 14:30.591
But it's so dark.

14:32.304 --> 14:34.524
I didn't like the dark either,

14:34.773 --> 14:36.618
until my dad found a cure.

14:37.416 --> 14:40.486
He made up a story called
"The Owl Who Says What."

14:40.623 --> 14:41.924
He even wrote a book about it.

14:42.650 --> 14:44.382
Owls say, "Who."

14:44.449 --> 14:46.534
Yeah, not this one.

14:46.718 --> 14:48.620
The other owls left him by himself

14:48.650 --> 14:51.553
alone in the dark,
because he was different.

14:51.723 --> 14:53.558
- Was he scared?
- Yeah,

14:53.698 --> 14:56.728
but he discovers a way
not to be afraid of the dark.

14:57.214 --> 14:58.862
How?

14:59.197 --> 15:01.198
I could read it to you if you want.

15:01.409 --> 15:03.050
I'm sure the bookstore has it.

15:03.186 --> 15:04.921
You want to go?

15:07.256 --> 15:08.724
We're gonna go to the bookstore.

15:10.718 --> 15:12.553
I guess. Sure.

15:23.659 --> 15:24.714
I'll tidy up.

15:35.122 --> 15:37.024
She adores her father.

15:39.704 --> 15:41.573
He must be a good guy.

15:43.475 --> 15:45.013
He is.

15:48.380 --> 15:50.482
How bad is it between you and him?

15:53.881 --> 15:55.826
Is it that obvious?

15:57.722 --> 15:59.768
I was married for 10 years.

16:00.194 --> 16:03.823
I mean, not married,
because we couldn't get married,

16:03.917 --> 16:07.565
but we lived together, and I loved her.

16:09.174 --> 16:13.054
But she was the most annoying
person I've ever met.

16:13.413 --> 16:15.843
I know a frustrated woman
when I see one.

16:21.179 --> 16:22.761
Kevin's a good person.

16:23.034 --> 16:26.777
He's kind and sensitive.

16:27.331 --> 16:29.620
He's patient. He's a great listener.

16:29.921 --> 16:31.979
He sounds awful.

16:40.128 --> 16:42.763
His love for Alex is endless.

16:42.951 --> 16:45.140
He needs her love to be the same.

16:45.381 --> 16:47.537
He needs it so much, he can't say no.

16:47.737 --> 16:49.490
He never could.

16:52.077 --> 16:54.230
And now, it put her in danger.

16:59.113 --> 17:00.996
I'm happy he's not here.

