23:13.972 --> 23:15.555
Did you hear something?

23:16.355 --> 23:17.745
It's fine.

23:18.167 --> 23:19.893
Let's reel it in.

23:25.528 --> 23:27.297
- You got it?
- There we go.

23:27.364 --> 23:28.465
Okay, okay.

23:28.567 --> 23:29.778
There she is.

23:32.062 --> 23:33.096
I'll get the door.

23:34.400 --> 23:36.669
"Then the owl said, 'Who are you to say

23:36.720 --> 23:38.522
I can't say "what" '?

23:38.900 --> 23:42.572
But the other owls
just said, 'Who, who, who.'"

23:42.979 --> 23:44.414
That's not nice of them.

23:46.211 --> 23:48.013
Okay, next one. Ready?

23:49.786 --> 23:51.821
- Oh, shit.
- Damn!

23:57.758 --> 24:00.063
Wait, wait. wait.
Stop, stop, stop! It's stuck.

24:04.067 --> 24:06.196
Hey, screw it. Yeah.

24:06.336 --> 24:07.931
Don't let go of the line.

24:08.595 --> 24:10.369
