Ted?

24:33.363 --> 24:34.664
Ted?

24:39.035 --> 24:40.604
Ted!

24:59.395 --> 25:01.771
Um, stay here.

25:06.730 --> 25:08.544
Ted!

25:08.698 --> 25:10.302
Help! Help!

25:18.196 --> 25:20.089
