25:37.513 --> 25:39.560
Oh, my God! It was an accident!

25:39.607 --> 25:41.029
I didn't mean to do it! I really didn't!

25:41.060 --> 25:42.999
- Where?
- Bookstore.

25:48.471 --> 25:50.674
Run!

26:00.814 --> 26:02.926
- Jesus.
- Somebody please help!

26:03.051 --> 26:05.046
Yeah, the Copeland girl.

26:05.113 --> 26:06.648
Alex, help!

26:06.735 --> 26:09.047
- Where are you?
- Lila!

26:09.184 --> 26:11.305
- Lila!
- Over here!

26:11.349 --> 26:12.493
Holy shit!

26:13.602 --> 26:15.358
What the fuck is that?

26:16.958 --> 26:19.749
Is she in there? Get out of my way!

26:19.811 --> 26:20.882
No, no, no. You can't! You can't!

26:20.913 --> 26:22.730
- Don't let it in!
- Lila! Lila!

26:22.797 --> 26:24.913
Don't! Look... Look at that!

26:24.988 --> 26:28.132
- We open the door, we all die!
- Lila, run! Help! No!

26:28.163 --> 26:29.569
Alex!

26:29.593 --> 26:30.779
Look, I didn't know she was in there.

26:30.804 --> 26:32.392
Mom!

26:33.006 --> 26:35.188
- You can't go in there. It's not safe!
- Lila!

26:35.935 --> 26:37.665
Run, baby!

26:38.512 --> 26:40.380
Run!

26:58.177 --> 26:59.812
No!

27:18.427 --> 27:20.185
Lila!

27:47.842 --> 27:48.952
Eve.

27:55.154 --> 27:56.969
You okay? Oh.

28:02.408 --> 28:05.196
You okay? What happened?

28:05.329 --> 28:07.110
I just...

28:07.696 --> 28:11.696
I... I fought it, hard as I could.

28:38.404 --> 28:40.404
I am concerned about her.

28:40.756 --> 28:42.951
She's always had some funny ideas.

28:44.416 --> 28:46.435
But she's hurting herself.

28:47.453 --> 28:51.360
Last night, she referred
to the spider as God.

28:53.425 --> 28:55.461
First the moth, then this.

28:55.528 --> 28:57.251
It is idolatry.

28:57.463 --> 29:00.287
If this is Judgment Day,
she will be judged for it.

29:00.668 --> 29:02.203
And if it's not?

29:03.949 --> 29:05.654
You haven't been out there,

29:06.098 --> 29:07.533
not the way I have.

29:08.028 --> 29:09.723
When I was,

29:10.466 --> 29:12.122
I felt something.

29:13.045 --> 29:14.520
What did you feel?

29:16.182 --> 29:17.583
That it knew me.

30:07.445 --> 30:08.501
I'm sorry.

30:09.602 --> 30:10.536
Please.

30:10.603 --> 30:12.104
I have to look out for my boy.

30:12.171 --> 30:13.482
You'd do the same.

30:13.542 --> 30:15.090
You have the only working car.

30:15.232 --> 30:17.067
You're my only chance.

30:17.276 --> 30:18.817
- You understand that?
- Yes, I do.

30:20.779 --> 30:22.181
Are you gonna tell him, or should I?

30:22.248 --> 30:23.616
Mia, I'm taking care of this.

30:23.682 --> 30:24.818
Well, if you were, we wouldn't have

30:24.873 --> 30:26.552
spent the night sleeping
in a goddamn minimart.

30:26.619 --> 30:28.487
There is nothing
that you can say to help.

30:32.725 --> 30:34.757
Look, your son is dead.

30:35.394 --> 30:36.495
We saw him.

30:39.265 --> 30:40.399
You're lying.

30:43.402 --> 30:45.590
I'm sorry, but it's the truth.

30:50.973 --> 30:52.975
You're lying.

30:53.292 --> 30:54.412
You're lying.

30:54.456 --> 30:55.991
You didn't see what we saw.

30:56.057 --> 30:57.726
If you had, you'd understand.

30:57.799 --> 30:59.736
No, you would have told me
when I showed you the photo.

30:59.790 --> 31:01.529
You're lying.
You made this up to get my car!

31:01.596 --> 31:04.065
I'm not gonna do it!
I'm gonna find my son!

31:04.132 --> 31:06.874
He's alive! I know it!

31:09.684 --> 31:10.885
Tell him.

31:15.670 --> 31:16.904
Tell him!

31:19.893 --> 31:21.440
He's dead.

31:21.994 --> 31:23.659
I told them not to tell you.

31:23.918 --> 31:25.878
Why?

31:26.549 --> 31:28.151
I didn't want to take away your hope.

31:28.390 --> 31:30.057
I'm sorry.

31:30.225 --> 31:32.033
- I truly am.
- You stop saying that.

31:32.080 --> 31:34.864
He's not coming back.
He's not, and you're stopping us from...

31:34.930 --> 31:36.049
Just shut up!

31:36.104 --> 31:37.736
You are not gonna get the car!

31:37.799 --> 31:39.367
You're not gonna get the car!

31:39.434 --> 31:42.337
I will kill you all, if I have to!

31:47.074 --> 31:48.243
Shoot him!

31:49.611 --> 31:52.280
Come on! Shoot him!

31:56.395 --> 31:58.164
I'm so sorry.

31:58.528 --> 32:00.263
I didn't mean to.

32:00.455 --> 32:01.856
Get the towel.

32:06.218 --> 32:07.452
Do you have a belt?

32:09.183 --> 32:11.118
Here, put pressure.

32:15.738 --> 32:18.273
If we don't get him
to a hospital, he's gonna die.

32:23.425 --> 32:24.679
I'm so sorry.

32:24.761 --> 32:26.663
But you have to understand,

32:26.982 --> 32:28.343
it really was an accident.

32:28.406 --> 32:30.156
We were trying to do
the right thing. We messed up.

32:30.226 --> 32:32.234
Shelley lost her little girl
because of it.

32:32.296 --> 32:33.488
And I'm so sorry.

32:33.555 --> 32:35.123
I promise. It'll never happen again.

32:35.190 --> 32:37.691
That's what you said after sending
my friends out in the mist.

32:39.330 --> 32:41.065
Don't look at me. I'm not the king.

32:41.296 --> 32:42.829
So what do we do?

32:43.188 --> 32:45.360
Zoe was closer to Ted than any of us.

32:45.492 --> 32:47.361
She should have a chance to speak.

32:50.998 --> 32:52.607
What do I think?

32:53.041 --> 32:56.701
Anyone who endangers the group
is thrown out!

32:56.803 --> 32:59.553
- Are those the rules, or aren't they?
- This is insane.

32:59.605 --> 33:01.040
I say we put it to a vote!

33:01.107 --> 33:02.608
Maybe we should wait...

33:03.713 --> 33:05.436
until the police get here.

33:05.587 --> 33:06.788
The police?

33:07.295 --> 33:09.912
That's who you're waiting for?
You want to wait for your dad?

33:10.016 --> 33:11.884
Well, tell me, what would he
do if he were here?

33:11.951 --> 33:13.986
Because the Officer Heisel
I know isn't a pussy like you.

33:14.053 --> 33:16.133
This should be decided by all of us.

33:16.393 --> 33:18.161
We put it to a vote, okay?

33:21.627 --> 33:26.535
Everyone in favor of forgiving
Vic for violating the rules,

33:26.791 --> 33:28.496
please raise your hands.

33:33.626 --> 33:36.165
All those in favor
of expelling Vic from the mall,

33:36.688 --> 33:39.376
per the rules
as agreed upon by the group.

33:45.450 --> 33:46.718
You're killing me.

33:50.450 --> 33:51.991
Would you grab
a hiking pack from the store

33:52.058 --> 33:53.359
and gather Vic's things for him?

33:54.573 --> 33:57.297
Put together, uh,
three days' provisions,

33:58.172 --> 34:01.461
a flashlight, and a means
of defending himself.

34:17.329 --> 34:18.617
Hello.

34:18.899 --> 34:20.531
There...

34:21.431 --> 34:24.456
Natalie, please. You're scaring my wife.

34:24.524 --> 34:27.097
Oh, please don't be afraid.

34:27.425 --> 34:29.027
I know these creatures.

34:29.063 --> 34:30.518
They would never harm us.

34:30.589 --> 34:32.090
You saw what happened to Mikhail.

34:32.297 --> 34:34.067
I'm sure it had a reason.

34:34.331 --> 34:36.793
Have you ever experienced nature
not having a reason?

34:37.469 --> 34:39.338
Mother Earth is never wrong.

34:39.405 --> 34:41.063
She knows what she's doing,

34:41.328 --> 34:43.571
and so will we if we observe her.

34:44.277 --> 34:46.649
Father, I... I beg you,

34:46.985 --> 34:49.815
the Bible warns
about the false prophets.

34:49.882 --> 34:53.085
She's worshipping a false god
in your church.

34:54.587 --> 34:56.188
I can't reach her.

34:57.590 --> 34:59.325
When you met me, I was unreachable.

35:03.496 --> 35:04.831
That was different.

35:04.897 --> 35:07.185
You knew exactly what you were doing.

35:07.600 --> 35:09.502
I'm sure to an outsider,
it would've looked cruel...

35:11.304 --> 35:13.429
but you reached me.

35:14.202 --> 35:18.804
Father, you reached me.

35:37.764 --> 35:40.057
I know that this may seem harsh,

35:41.257 --> 35:44.130
but if I can save your soul,
it will be worth it.

35:45.705 --> 35:47.474
I need you to kill the spider.

35:47.640 --> 35:49.361
I will do no such thing.

35:49.415 --> 35:53.736
Please. Kill the spider.

35:54.228 --> 35:56.677
- Save yourself.
- I will not kill her.

35:56.740 --> 35:58.552
Mrs. Raven, I'm not punishing you.

35:58.654 --> 36:00.326
I am trying to help you.

36:00.834 --> 36:05.388
Now, please kill the spider.

36:05.451 --> 36:06.759
Absolutely not!

36:06.826 --> 36:08.693
No! No!

36:09.037 --> 36:09.971
Please!

36:10.163 --> 36:12.615
No! No!

36:55.041 --> 36:56.576
Jay, come on. You were accused, too.

36:56.609 --> 36:58.383
They didn't throw you out.
I made a mistake.

36:58.408 --> 37:01.114
Everyone makes mistakes.
This isn't right! Please!

37:01.180 --> 37:02.419
This is what we voted for.

37:03.216 --> 37:05.372
We have to be safe in here.

37:06.052 --> 37:07.787
Get your hands off me! Let me go!

37:30.777 --> 37:32.145
Fuck you!

37:32.531 --> 37:34.400
Fuck all of you!

37:41.054 --> 37:44.990
I know that my actions today

37:45.615 --> 37:48.545
appeared cold and callous,

37:49.170 --> 37:52.577
but I beg of you to understand
that they are the opposite,

37:53.499 --> 37:55.170
that they are an act of charity,

37:56.202 --> 38:01.240
of helping a lost soul
find her way to Heaven.

38:01.307 --> 38:02.942
You asked me
what I thought was happening.

38:03.377 --> 38:04.777
I'm not asking anymore.

38:10.316 --> 38:11.684
I would like to answer.

38:11.971 --> 38:13.281
We're not interested.

38:28.722 --> 38:32.535
No one is interested!

38:35.208 --> 38:36.477
I am.

38:46.853 --> 38:48.154
I am.

39:21.587 --> 39:23.356
That's okay.

39:24.690 --> 39:26.359
I lied.

39:28.194 --> 39:29.629
What do you mean?

39:31.030 --> 39:32.579
I didn't fight.

39:33.025 --> 39:34.509
I didn't do anything.

39:34.667 --> 39:36.798
I just waited for it to kill me.

39:37.283 --> 39:40.329
It came, it looked at me, and it left.

39:44.845 --> 39:46.807
Why did't it want me?

40:06.733 --> 40:08.234
Shelley, I'm so sorry.

40:09.865 --> 40:11.833
I don't want to be
with those people anymore.

40:12.502 --> 40:13.798
You can stay here.

40:14.719 --> 40:16.988
Kyle, will you get
a blanket for Shelley?

40:17.375 --> 40:19.010
Here. You can have mine.

40:22.982 --> 40:24.417
Thanks.

40:34.167 --> 40:35.435
You were right.

40:36.025 --> 40:37.717
Alex is a liar.

40:45.831 --> 40:47.231
We need to go.

40:47.801 --> 40:49.520
I need to look for my son.

40:49.728 --> 40:54.728
Come with us.

40:54.753 --> 40:56.121
You should get in the car now.

40:56.159 --> 40:57.179
Clay.

40:58.870 --> 41:00.448
He's out there.

41:01.268 --> 41:02.736
